				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/equity/programs-and-reports/truth-and-reconciliation-at-ryerson/truth-reconciliation-ryerson-consultations.jpg" alt="Elder Joanna Dallaire sitting with others around a table at Ryerson community consultations, the Eagle Staff stands nearby"/>




					 
