<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="1d38bdce-30da-497c-9a00-2b90d1f76ab9" >

    <h4>Plaque unveiling&nbsp;</h4> 
<p>Students and alumni joined in the unveiling of a new plaque to be installed next to the Egerton Ryerson statue on Gould Street. The plaque acknowledges Ryerson’s connection to residential schools and is a reminder of the university’s commitment to Truth and Reconciliation and to respectful relationships with Indigenous communities.</p>
    





</div>
